                            <comment id="56321" author="ihara" created="Mon, 15 Apr 2013 13:44:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Yang thanks for your confirmation. You are right and I also confirmed that this patch included in kernel-2.6.18-redhat.patch of the latest RHEL5.9&apos;s kernel rpm. So, we don&apos;t need this patch for the lustre kernel anymore since it&apos;s fixed in the base kernel.&lt;br/&gt;
Please close this ticket. thanks again!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
